  "method": [
    "Take a saucepan and heat the oil.",
    "Add onions. Cook for around 2 minutes.",
    "Add jalapenos and garlic.",
    "Add tomatoes, chicken broth, and beans to the pot. Bring it to boil.",
    "Lower the heat and add chicken breasts, and cook for 20-25 minutes.",
    "When it is cook, take it out and let it cool so you could easily shred it.",
    "Add fresh cilantro and lime juice.",
    "Take a bowl and add shredded chicken in it. Pour soup over it.",
    "Put a grilled tortilla, lime wedge, cheese, and avocado slices on top,",
    "and serve."
